explanations.description: A wide range of words or phrases that express strong or emphatic positive or negative reactions, descriptions, or conditions, often related to abilities, circumstances, or characteristics, and frequently taking the form of adjectives, nouns, or adverbs with distinctive suffixes or prefixes (e.g. "phenomenal", "phenomenon", "phenom", "horrrendous", "fabulously", "commendable", "abysmal", "hysterical", "homophobic", "nostalgic").
